      "content": "Hold on a second. Before we push this update through, I need you to run a simulation of what this re-weighting will do to our overall procurement reliability. The concern from the logistics team is that shifting the weight away from these 'legacy' firms might cause a massive drop in contract fulfillment speed and reliability. If the system's efficiency tanked because we prioritized diversity over established performance metrics, that's on us. \n\nGive me the breakdown. How much of a risk is this actually going to pose to our mission-critical operations if we move away from the current data-driven model?",
